lenced%20the%20ambient%20hum%20was%20scarily%20good.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20raised%20the%20airplane%20cabin%20noise%20to%2062%20decibels%2C%20at%20the%20same%20distance%2C%20and%20I%20was%20able%20to%20make%20that%20noise%20completely%20disappear%20with%20music%20playing%20at%2025%25%20volume.%20With%20music%20playing%20at%2035%25%20volume%20and%20ANC%20on%2C%20the%20earbuds%20were%20able%20to%20block%20out%20cabin%20noise%20at%2070%20decibels%20from%2018%20inches%20away.%20This%20level%20of%20noise-canceling%20is%20impressive%20and%20better%20than%20any%20I've%20heard%20from%20rival%20brands.%20But%20as%20far%20as%20I%20could%20discern%2C%20the%20first-gen%20QC%20Ultra%20Earbuds%20deliver%20similar%20results.%20So%2C%20while%20this%20new%20model%20carries%20over%20the%20first-gen%20earbuds'%20incredible%20ANC%20performance%2C%20its%20improvements%20are%20subtle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20important%20to%20note%20that%20good%20ANC%20performance%20is%20heavily%20reliant%20on%20getting%20a%20proper%20fit%20and%20seal%20with%20each%20earbud.%20Without%20a%20tight%20seal%2C%20the%20ANC%20technology%20can't%20fully%20do%20its%20job%2C%20and%20there%20will%20be%20some%20noise%20leakage.%20To%20help%20with%20this%2C%20the%20earbuds%20come%20with%20additional%20ear%20tips%20and%20stability%20bands%20in%20the%20box.%20There's%20also%20an%20ear-fit%20test%20in%20the%20Bose%20app%20to%20help%20you%20confirm%20that%20sound%20isn't%20leaking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222047%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tech%20writer%20Tyler%20Hayes%20wearing%20a%20pair%20of%20Bose%20QuietComfort%20Ultra%20Earbuds%20(2nd%20Gen).%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68af5f18cfc04e97619c26f9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221535%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20earbuds%20support%20an%20Immersion%20mode%20that%20can%20reposition%20sounds%20based%20on%20your%20head%20movements%2C%20but%20we%20prefer%20to%20leave%20this%20setting%20off.%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20default%2C%20the%20earbuds%20let%20you%20choose%20between%20three%20audio%20modes%20in%20the%20app%3A%20Quiet%2C%20Aware%2C%20and%20Immersion.%20Quiet%20has%20the%20highest%20level%20of%20ANC.%20But%20if%20you're%20sensitive%20to%20heavy%20doses%20of%20noise%20cancellation%2C%20you%20can%20also%20create%20your%20own%20custom%20mode%20with%2010%20levels%20of%20adjustment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Aware%20mode%20deactivates%20ANC%20and%20uses%20the%20earbuds'%20microphones%20to%20enable%20a%20transparency%20feature%20that%20lets%20in%20outside%20sound.%20This%20mode%20also%20uses%20Bose's%20ActiveSense%20tech%20to%20prevent%20sudden%20spikes%20in%20outside%20noise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20Immersion%20is%20Bose's%20spatial%20audio%20mode.%20This%20adds%20depth%20to%20music%20(kind%20of%20like%20a%20faux%20surround%20sound%20mode)%20by%20positioning%20audio%20around%20you.%20The%20mode%20uses%20100%25%20ANC%20by%20default%20and%20repositions%20sounds%20based%20on%20your%20orientation%2C%20so%20if%20you%20shift%20your%20head%2C%20the%20audio%20tracks%20your%20movements.%20You%20can%20also%20disable%20head-tracking%20to%20create%20a%20fixed%20sense%20of%203D%20audio%2C%20so%20the%20sounds%20stay%20in%20the%20same%20place%20when%20you%20move%20your%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20hard%20to%20predict%20what%20people%20will%20think%20of%20Immersion%20until%20they%20try%20it.%20However%2C%20this%20kind%20of%20processing%20isn't%20for%20me.%20I%20never%20found%20it%20to%20actively%20ruin%20songs%20or%20shows%2C%20but%20I%20prefer%20the%20way%20standard%20stereo%20playback%20sounded%20for%20most%20content.%20If%20you%20do%20play%20around%20with%20the%20Immersion%20setting%2C%20just%20be%20aware%20that%20turning%20it%20on%20does%20use%20more%20battery%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20of%20which%2C%20the%20earbuds%20are%20rated%20for%20up%20to%20six%20hours%20of%20use%2C%20which%20is%20the%20same%20amount%20as%20the%20first-generation%20model.%20That's%20a%20decent%20number%2C%20but%20not%20as%20high%20as%20some%20competing%20earbuds%2C%20like%20the%20premium%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-1511033933479-20%26h%3D3a0f6392a6efb4f4bfd9de3b62a7b7ad5b7657f794af7dee1a2788b5b0e43c49%26postID%3D68af27dcbdd07b99f0c4cd38%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fbose-quietcomfort-ultra-earbuds-2nd-gen-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252Fdp%252FB0DSCN2KPR%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETechnics%20EAH-AZ100%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20can%20offer%20up%20to%2010%20hours%20with%20ANC%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226e0ddd65-a9e0-4195-8bb7-50d1d78afb0f%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Call%20quality%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECall%20quality%20is%20also%20exceptional%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221696%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20close-up%20of%20a%20hand%20holding%20the%20Bose%20QC%20Ultra%202nd%20Gen%20earbuds.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68af6006a17a8c5b40539ba2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221272%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20earbuds'%20integrated%20microphones%20deliver%20fantastic%20call%20quality%20that%20isolates%20your%20voice%20while%20still%20maintaining%20a%20natural%20tone.%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20microphone%20quality%20rarely%20gets%20the%20spotlight%20it%20deserves%2C%20it's%20a%20critical%20part%20of%20modern%20earbuds%20and%20headphones.%20Many%20people%20use%20their%20earbuds%20for%20phone%20calls%2C%20video%20conferences%2C%20and%20FaceTime%20chats%2C%20so%20good%20microphone%20performance%20ensures%20that%20users%20are%20easy%20to%20hear%20and%20sound%20natural.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second-gen%20QC%20Ultra%20Earbuds%20have%20a%20new%20feature%20to%20boost%20call%20quality.%20It's%20called%20Bose%20SpeechClarity%2C%20and%20it's%20currently%20exclusive%20to%20this%20model.%20SpeechClarity%20uses%20AI-based%20proprietary%20technology%20to%20suppress%20background%20noise.%20Though%20Bose%20is%20far%20from%20the%20only%20headphone%20brand%20to%20offer%20a%20feature%20like%20this%2C%20few%20competitors%20pull%20it%20off%20as%20well%20as%20Bose%20does%20with%20these%20earbuds%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20recorded%20my%20voice%20in%20several%20quiet%20and%20loud%20environments%20to%20get%20a%20sense%20of%20how%20I%20would%20sound%20during%20calls.%20Compared%20to%20the%20first-generation%20earbuds%2C%20the%20second-generation%20QC%20Ultra%20sound%20noticeably%20better%2C%20with%20a%20fuller%20tone.%20Even%20in%20a%20noisy%20environment%2C%20they%20managed%20to%20keep%20my%20voice%20present%2C%20full%2C%20and%20extremely%20clear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20recently%20conducted%20the%20same%20set%20of%20tests%20with%20a%20similar%20feature%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fnothing-headphone-1-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENothing%20Headphone%20(1)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20that%20brand's%20effect%20was%20too%20aggressive%20and%20clipped%20some%20of%20the%20words%20I%20was%20saying.%20That%20was%20never%20the%20case%20with%20Bose's%20earbuds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228aeb3bcf-8790-4721-82aa-167b148bb148%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Should%20you%20buy%20them%3F%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EShould%20you%20buy%20the%20Bose%20QuietComfort%20Ultra%20Earbuds%20(2nd%20Gen)%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222189%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20pair%20of%20Bose%20QC%20Ultra%20Earbuds%202nd%20Gen%20in%20their%20case.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68af6061194a2d49b8af4dc7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221459%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20second-generation%20Bose%20QC%20Ultra%20are%20the%20new%20noise-canceling%20earbuds%20t