0and%20the%20long-term%20interests%20of%20the%20American%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20pressure%20on%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20comes%20as%20he%20seeks%20lower%20interest%20rates%2C%20which%20he%20believes%20will%20help%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-firing-lisa-cook-fed-independence-dollar-treasury-stocks-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehis%20economic%20agenda%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20president%20said%20he%20was%20terminating%20Cook%20from%20her%20position%20for%20%26quot%3Bcause%26quot%3B%20based%20on%20a%20criminal%20referral%20by%20one%20of%20his%20political%20appointees%2C%20Federal%20Housing%20Finance%20Agency%20Director%20Bill%20Pulte%2C%20who%20said%20Cook%20lied%20on%20mortgage%20paperwork.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20conduct%20at%20issue%20exhibits%20the%20sort%20of%20gross%20negligence%20in%20financial%20transactions%20that%20calls%20into%20question%20your%20competence%20and%20trustworthiness%20as%20a%20financial%20regulator%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECook's%20Thursday%20lawsuit%20says%20the%20allegations%20are%20%26quot%3Bunsubstantiated%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20even%20if%20they%20were%20true%20they%20do%20not%20reach%20the%20legal%20standard%20of%20for-cause%20removal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPresident%20Trump%20does%20not%20have%20the%20power%20to%20unilaterally%20redefine%20'cause'%20%E2%80%94%20completely%20unmoored%20to%20caselaw%2C%20history%2C%20and%20tradition%20%E2%80%94%20and%20conclude%2C%20without%20evidence%2C%20that%20he%20has%20found%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECook%20is%20represented%20by%20Abbe%20Lowell%20and%20Norm%20Eisen%2C%20two%20attorneys%20who%20have%20criticized%20Trump%20and%20represent%20numerous%20government%20employees%20wh