Fdelhi-warrior-moms-fight-air-pollution-climate-change-for-better-future-of-children%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esnowballed%20into%20a%20people%E2%80%99s%20movement%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%20the%20banner%20of%20Pali%20Hill%20Residents%E2%80%99%20Association%20(PHRA)%2C%20as%20more%20women%20and%20men%20joined%20hands.%20A%20managing%20committee%20was%20elected%20with%20Sumi%20Mehta%20as%20the%20chairperson%20and%20Dr%20Amitav%20Shukla%20as%20the%20secretary.%20Since%20then%2C%20committees%20have%20changed%2C%20but%20the%20good%20work%20has%20carried%20on.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0It%20has%20been%20no%20cake%20walk%2C%20say%20PHRA%20members%2C%20who%20had%20to%20work%20around%20the%20clock%2C%20meeting%20residents%2C%20civic%20officials%2C%20police%20officers%20and%20others%20repeatedly.%C2%A0%E2%80%9CTo%20me%20it%20was%20a%20mission%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sumi.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20an%20enthusiastic%20and%20supportive%20team%20of%20women.%C2%A0%20We%20used%20to%20spend%20two%20hours%20every%20day%20going%20around%20meeting%20residents%2C%20civic%2C%20police%20officials%2C%20etc.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22pali%20hill%20residents%20association%20%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fpali-hill-1-1690871233.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%C2%A0It%20has%20been%20no%20cake%20walk%2C%20say%20PHRA%20members%2C%20who%20had%20to%20work%20around%20the%20clock%2C%20meeting%20residents%2C%20civic%20officials%2C%20police%20officers%20and%20others%20repeatedly.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98They%20were%20not%20convinced%20that%20women%20like%20us%20would%20achieve%20anything.%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrent%20PHRA%20secretary%20Madhu%20Poplai%2C%20who%20has%20been%20carrying%20forward%20the%20mission%20since%20Sumi%20left%20in%202004%2C%20concurs.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20those%20days%2C%20we%20used%20to%20visit%20our%20ward%20office%20and%20police%20station%20regularly%2C%20like%20how%20people%20visit%20temples.%20We%20would%20drop%20our%20children%20off%20at%20school%20and%20then%20proceed%20together.%E2%80%9D%20Madhu%20has%20been%20a%20PHRA%20member%20since%20its%20inception%2C%20and%20has%20been%20holding%20the%20post%20of%20either%20Chairman%20or%20Secretary%20for%20the%20last%2016%20years%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoing%20in%20groups%20is%20effective%2C%20says%20Sumi.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20working%20for%20a%20public%20cause%2C%20always%20work%20and%20move%20around%20in%20groups%2C%20more%20so%20when%20meeting%20officials.%20Keep%20on%20knocking%20on%20their%20doors%20till%20they%20hear%20you.%20Involve%20housewives%20and%20retired%20men.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20funding%2C%20PHRA%20originally%20requested%20residents%20to%20contribute%20Rs%20360%20per%20flat%20per%20annum%20and%20Rs%201%2C200%20per%20bungalow%20per%20annum.%20Today%2C%20they%20have%20raised%20the%20amount%20to%20Rs%20900%20and%20Rs%202%2C500%2C%20respectively.%20%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20people%20thought%20we%20were%20collecting%20money%20to%20have%20kitty%20parties%20or%20for%20our%20household%20expenses.%20They%20were%20not%20convinced%20that%20a%20few%20women%20like%20us%20would%20achieve%20anything%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Sanchali%20Sarkar%2C%20present%20managing%20committee%20member%2C%20who%20was%20among%20the%20team%20that%20went%20house%20to%20house%20to%20gather%20funds.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20the%20managing%20committee%20with%2021%20members%20(18%20women%20and%203%20men)%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F288533%2Fhow-to-volunteer-programmes-in-himachal-pradesh-tibetan-refugees%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethere%20are%20many%20volunteers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20largely%20women.%C2%A0%20Pali%20Hill%20has%2079%20buildings%20and%2023%20bungalows.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20housing%20societies%20collect%20the%20money%20from%20their%20members%20and%20pay%20it%20to%20PHRA%2C%20bungalow%20owners%20pay%20it%20to%20us%20individually.%C2%A0%20The%20compliance%20level%20is%2095%20to%2098%20percent%20now.%20People%20are%20trusting%20us%2C%20and%20donations%20from%20individuals%20and%20corporates%20are%20also%20coming%20in%2C%E2%80%9D%20reveals%20Madhu.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20men%2C%20too%2C%20have%20been%20playing%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20Pali%20Hill%E2%80%99s%20transformation.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20all%20can%2C%20and%20should%2C%20find%20time%20to%20work%20for%20the%20betterment%20of%20our%20people%20and%20our%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20avers%20Sonu%20Chagti%2C%20the%20present%20managing%20committee%20member%20who%20looks%20after%20roads%2C%20security%2C%20and%20the%20environment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22pali%20hill%20residents%20association%20%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fpali-hill-2-1690871313.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAnd%20men%2C%20too%2C%20have%20been%20playing%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20Pali%20Hill%E2%80%99s%20transformation.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPHRA%20achieved%20a%20significant%20milestone%20when%20its%20garbage%20management%20led%20to%20the%20production%20of%20energy%20from%20wet%20garbage.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20work%20was%20a%20decade-long%20endeavour%2C%20starting%20with%20door-to-door%20garbage%20collection%2C%20where%20members%20worked%20towards%20creating%20awareness%20about%20segregation%2C%20overcoming%20initial%20resistance%2C%20and%20finally%20implementing%20it%20with%20BMC%E2%80%99s%20help.%20%E2%80%9CBy%202019%2C%20we%20were%20segregating%20almost%2090%25%20of%20our%20waste.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20garbage%20going%20to%20the%20dumpi