8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eshaky%20finances%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Burning%20Man%20appears%20to%20have%20drawn%20out%20many%20of%20Silicon%20Valley's%20leaders.%20Those%20left%20on%20the%20ground%20in%20the%20Bay%20Area%20said%20they've%20found%20quieter%20highways%2C%20easier%20dinner%20reservations%2C%20and%20a%20bounty%20of%20out-of-office%20emails.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20many%2C%20life%20in%20the%20fast-paced%20Silicon%20Valley%20slows%20down%20a%20bit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVijay%20Chattha%20has%20fewer%20calls%20this%20week.%20He%20runs%20communications%20firm%20VSC%20and%20its%20investment%20arm%2C%20VSC%20Ventures.%20He%20said%20he%20can%20always%20tell%20when%20someone%20is%20at%20Burning%20Man.%20Anytime%20a%20%26quot%3Bdecision-maker%26quot%3B%20is%20gone%20around%20the%20festival%20dates%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%94%C2%A0so%2C%20a%20founder%20or%20CEO%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0they're%20probably%20at%20the%20Playa%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20the%20people%20that%20go%2C%20at%20least%20in%20tech%2C%20are%20in%20their%20regular%20weeks%20probably%20quite%20intense%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Chattha%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20cortisol%20levels%20are%20low%20this%20week.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%229023%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Playa%20at%20Burning%20Man%202023%2C%20photographed%20from%20the%20air.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b04b89194a2d49b8af5559%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225541%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Playa%20at%20Burning%20Man%202023%2C%20photographed%20from%20the%20air.%3Cp%3EGetty%2FMaxar%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20some%20added%20perks%20to%20having%20fewer%20techies%20in%20the%20city.%20Chattha%20said%20it's%20easier%20to%20get%20a%20restaurant%20reservation.%20Driving%20into%20San%20Francisco%20from%20Marin%2C%20he%20noticed%20less%20traffic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlison%20Berman%20also%20noticed%20fewer%20cars%20on%20the%20road.%20She's%20spent%20the%20last%2010%20years%20hopping%20around%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20mostly%20working%20in%20climate%20tech.%20She's%20not%20a%20fan%20of%20Burning%20Man%20and%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fultrarich-burning-man-attendees-face-protesters-private-jets-plastic-use-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecarbon%20footprint%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20despite%20its%20%26quot%3Bleave%20no%20trace%26quot%3B%20mantra.%20Still%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Emost%20of%20Berman's%20friends%20are%20there%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20kind%20of%20a%20ghost%20town%20over%20Burning%20Man%2C%20where%20founders%20clear%20out%2C%20investors%20clear%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20Berman%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20notice%20it%20immediately%20in%20the%20decrease%20in%20traffic%2C%20which%20is%20great%20for%20the%20commute%2C%20but%20also%20you%20get%20a%20lot%20of%20out-of-office%20replies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20it's%20one%20of%20two%20major%20events%20that%20push%20many%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%20offline%3A%20Burning%20Man%20and%20Christmas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20founders%20looking%20to%20raise%20capital%2C%20Burning%20Man%20is%20often%20considered%20an%20off%20period.%20Ron%20Wiener%20runs%20startup%20accelerator%20Venture%20Mechanics.%20His%20advice%20to%20the%20accelerator's%20founders%3A%20Be%20ready%20for%20Labor%20Day%2C%20when%20everyone%20comes%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20ordinarily%20emailing%20VCs%20continuously%20and%20trying%20to%20get%20speakers%20for%20events%20or%20judges%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI've%20been%20fundraising%20for%2041%20years.%20I%20know%20this%20time%20of%20year%20is%20dead.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBurning%20Man%20also%20coincides%20with%20a%20common%20time%20to%20take%20a%20summer%20vacation%2C%20and%20with%20college%20move-ins%20for%20parents.%20Wiener%20said%20it%20creates%20the%20perfect%20storm%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bsuper%20dead%26quot%3B%20week.%3C