3ESome%20investors%20share%20that%20view.%20On%20Amazon's%20earnings%20call%20last%20month%2C%20Morgan%20Stanley%20analyst%20Brian%20Nowak%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-tumbles-ceo-andy-jassy-aws-cloud-ai-growth-concerns-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epressed%3C%2Fa%3E%20CEO%20Andy%20Jassy%20on%20Wall%20Street's%20%26quot%3Bnarrative%20right%20now%20that%20AWS%20is%20falling%20behind%26quot%3B%20in%20AI%20and%20fears%20of%20losing%20market%20share%20to%20rivals.%20Jassy's%20response%20fell%20flat%2C%20sending%20Amazon's%20stock%20lower%20during%20the%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20intends%20to%20tackle%20these%20concerns.%20According%20to%20the%20document%2C%20the%20company%20will%20refine%20its%20%26quot%3Bcompensation%20and%20location%20strategy%26quot%3B%20and%20host%20more%20events%20designed%20to%20highlight%20its%20generative%20AI%20capabilities.%20It%20also%20intends%20to%20set%20up%20dedicated%20recruiting%20teams%20for%20generative%20AI%20within%20business%20units%20like%20AWS%20to%20boost%20efficiency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225ce295d2-bbf1-41c2-b82a-9a744e6553f4%5C%22%3E'Hubs'%20constrain%20talent%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Amazon%20employees%20at%20company%20headquarters%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F626bfee086fa90001905cc29%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221687%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHundreds%20of%20tech%20workers%20gather%20outside%20the%20Amazon%20Spheres%20during%20a%20Climate%20Strike%20walkout%20and%20march%20in%20Seattle%2C%20Washington%2C%20U.S.%20September%2020%2C%202019.%3Cp%3EREUTERS%2FLindsey%20Wasson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20point%20of%20contention%20is%20Amazon's%20aggressive%20return-to-office%20mandate%2C%20which%20has%20already%20caused%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-rto-issues-space-security-productivity-2