n%20easily%20go%20grab%20a%20banana%2C%20but%20you're%20sticking%20with%20oranges%2C%20or%20eating%20only%20Chiquita%20bananas%20despite%20a%20generic%20brand%20sitting%20right%20next%20to%20them.%20Or%20in%20a%20non-banana%20example%2C%20you%20know%2C%20like%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20many%20consumers%20are%20facing%20is%20%3Cem%3Ecoerced%3C%2Fem%3E%20loyalty%20%E2%80%94%20barriers%20that%20keep%20people%20from%20changing%20things%20up%20or%20trying%20out%20competitors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20primary%20way%20companies%20rope%20people%20in%20is%20switching%20costs%2C%20which%20fall%20into%20three%20buckets%2C%20Fader%20explains.%20Some%20are%20financial%20%E2%80%94%20cancellation%20fees%2C%20lost%20airline%20miles.%20Others%20are%20procedural%20%E2%80%94%20there%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20tedious%2C%20time-consuming%20steps%20to%20switch%20from%20one%20mobile%20phone%20carrier%20to%20another.%20Finally%2C%20costs%20can%20be%20relationship-oriented%20%E2%80%94%20you%20know%20your%20dentist%20or%20hairstylist%20doesn't%20do%20the%20best%20job%2C%20but%20you've%20been%20going%20there%20forever%2C%20or%20you%20buy%20yet%20another%20iPhone%20because%20you're%20afraid%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-iphone-doj-lawsuit-antitrust-green-bubble-samsung-stigma-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edreaded%20green-text%20stigma%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20really%20is%20the%20case%20that%20the%20company%20kind%20of%20knows%20that%20they%20have%20you%20hostage%2C%26quot%3B%20Fader%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20why%20some%20companies%20make%20it%20so%20hard%20for%20you%20to%20cancel%20(and%20are%20fighting%20so%20hard%20against%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fftc-blocks-subscription-trap-click-to-cancel-ftc-rule-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFederal%20Trade%20Commission's%20click-to-cancel%20rule%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20would%20make%20quitting%20easier).%20Many%2