%20that%20a%20fair%20number%20of%20companies%20engage%20in%2C%20especially%20if%20the%20focus%20is%20getting%20people%20in%20the%20door%20and%20not%20worrying%20about%20what%20happens%20next.%20%26quot%3BThe%20worst%20thing%20that%20can%20happen%20to%20a%20bad%20product%20is%20good%20marketing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EConsumers%20do%20have%20agency%20in%20this.%20As%20much%20as%20all%20of%20our%20parents%20drilled%20into%20our%20heads%20as%20kids%20that%20we%20couldn't%20be%20quitters%2C%20you%20can%20indeed%20quit%2C%20even%20if%20the%20company%20makes%20it%20annoying%20to%20do%20so.%20And%20hey%2C%20you%20may%20not%20even%20have%20to%20cut%20ties%20entirely%20%E2%80%94%20you%20may%20just%20have%20to%20threaten%20to.%20Businesses%20often%20offer%20discounts%20or%20lower%20prices%20if%20you%20say%20you%20might%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMatt%20Schulz%2C%20the%20author%20of%20%26quot%3BAsk%20Questions%2C%20Save%20Money%2C%20Make%20More%2C%26quot%3B%20points%20out%20that%20you%20can%20also%20ask%20politely.%20You'd%20be%20surprised%20how%20much%20success%20you%20may%20have%20by%20calling%20your%20credit%20card%20company%20to%20ask%20for%20a%20lower%20interest%20rate%20or%20seeing%20whether%20the%20gym%20won't%20cut%20you%20a%20break%20on%20your%20monthly%20payment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20truth%20is%20that%20so%20many%20more%20things%20than%20people%20realize%20are%20negotiable%2C%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20times%2C%20it%20kind%20of%20comes%20down%20to%20doing%20the%20homework%20and%20knowing%20what%20the%20deals%20are%20for%20the%20new%20customer%20and%20asking%20for%20those%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20in%20the%20company's%20interest%20to%20keep%20you%20around%20and%20keep%20you%20happy%2C%20because%20the%20longer%20you're%20there%2C%20the%20more%20money%20they%20make%20of%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20to%20airlines%2C%20Leff%20says%20to%20just%20earn%20points%20on%20all%20the%20airlines%20you%20fly%20on%20%E2%80%94%20at%20some%20point%2C%20you'll%20probably%20be%20able%20to%20use%20them.%20You%20can%20look%20into%20credit%20cards%20where%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-cards%2Fchase-ultimate-rewards-points-transfer-partners%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epoints%20are%20transferable%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20airlines%2C%20but%20you%20may%20just%20be%20better%20off%20getting%20a%20cash-back%20card%20and%20accepting%20that%20airline%20loyalty%20is%20a%20thing%20of%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20isn't%20loyalty%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20fake%20loyalty.%20Sometimes%2C%20companies%20themselves%20don't%20know%20whether%20their%20customers%20like%20them%20or%20are%20trapped.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20now%20and%20again%2C%20they%20should%20have%20customer%20amnesty.%20Let's%20find%20out%20who's%20staying%20with%20us%20for%20the%20right%20reasons%20and%20who's%20staying%20with%20us%20just%20because%20of%20switching%20costs%2C%26quot%3B%20Fader%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsumers%20might%20not%20even%20know%20whether%20they're%20truly%20loyal%2C%20either.%20If%20switching%20costs%20were%20lowered%2C%20we%20could%20be%20in%20for%20some%20surprises.%20Fader%20notes%20that%20the%20mobile%20carriers%20fought%20tooth%20and%20nail%20against%20phone%20number%20portability%2C%20which%20allows%20people%20to%20keep%20their%20number%20even%20as%20they%20switch%20networks%2C%20but%20when%20it%20was%20finally%20allowed%2C%20most%20people%20didn't%20make%20a%20jump.%20There%20are%20plenty%20of%20loyalty%20programs%20and%20products%20that%20work%20well%20and%20that%20consumers%20would%20probably%20pay%20more%20for%20if%20pushed%2C%20Fader%20adds.%20He%20points%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flinkedin%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELinkedIn%20Premium%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20may%20not%20be%20worth%20it%20for%20most%20people%20but%20definitely%20is%20for%20super-users%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fhow-to-cancel-amazon-prime%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmazon%20Prime%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20does%20keep%20getting%20more%20expensive%20but%20at%20this%20point%20is%20%26quot%3Bjust%20the%20cost%20of%20being%20a%20human%20being%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20that%20you%20should%20avoid%20loyalty%20programs%20altogether%2C%20but%20you're%20going%20to%20want%20to%20read%20the%20fine%20print.%20Keep%20an%20eye%20on%20all%20your%20bills%2C%20and%20if%20they%20start%20to%20increase%2C%20figure%20out%20why.%20Try%20out%20new%20products%20and%20services%2C%20and%20if%20the%20new%20thing%20is%20better%20and%20cheaper%2C%20switch%20to%20it%2C%20even%20if%20it%20means%20an%20hour%20(and%20hopefully%20no%20more)%20on%20the%20phone.%20But%20it's%20always%20important%20to%20remember%20that%20a%20company%20won't%20love%20you%20back.%20It%20loves%20its%20shareholders.%20So%20go%20ahead%20and%20cheat%20if%20you%20want%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Femily-stewart%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EEmily%20Stewart%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20correspondent%20at%20Business%20Insider%2C%20writing%20about%20business%20and%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fconsumer-loyalty-dead-airline-miles-internet-company-car-insurance-prices-2025-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1756368242000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68af4ee5194a2d49b8af4b8d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fconsumer-loyalty-dead-airline-miles-internet-company-car-insurance-prices-2025-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Airlines%2C%20banks%2C%20and%20internet%20providers%20are%20taking%20advantage%20of%20people's%20unwillingnes