0species%20that%20has%20been%20existing%20for%20over%20120%20million%20years%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F201846%2Fodisha-olive-ridley-turtles-india-rescue-how-to-bichi-bhai-un-award-hero%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erequire%20a%20helping%20hand%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20half%20a%20century%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20story%20of%20the%20last%20500%20years%20for%20turtles%20is%20devastating%2C%20and%20now%20we%20are%20having%20to%20bring%20in%20a%20human%20hand%20of%20conservation%20to%20keep%20the%20species%20alive%20from%20our%20ways%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Arun%20Venkataramanan%2C%20a%20trustee%20and%20coordinator%20at%20SSTCN.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20the%20destroyers.%20We%20are%20the%20ones%20responsible%20for%20this.%20What%E2%80%99s%20happening%20now%20is%20that%20we%20are%20the%20saviours%20also%2C%20right%3F%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Arun%2C%20who%20now%20coordinates%20with%20like-minded%20volunteers%20who%20have%20understood%20this%20ground%20reality%20for%20the%20tiny%20turtles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FMervin-Feature-image-99-1743258466.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Arun%20addressing%20the%20people%20before%20the%20turtle%20walks%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FMervin-Feature-image-99-1743258466.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FMervin-Feature-image-99-1743258466-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FMervin-Feature-image-99-1743258466-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FMervin-Feature-image-99-1743258466-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F