gy)%20livelihood%20technologies%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20hydroponic%20fodder%20systems%20and%20solar%20dryers.%20This%20is%20in%20line%20with%20an%20ISBR%20study%20highlighting%20the%20rise%20of%20green%20entrepreneurship.%20It%20also%20ties%20into%20a%20report%20that%20positions%20the%20adoption%20of%20cleaner%20technologies%20through%20the%20MSE-GIFT%20(Green%20and%20Inclusive%20Finance%20for%20Transformation)%20Scheme%20as%20the%20next%20big%20step.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20states%20that%20from%202023%20to%202026%2C%20a%20total%20of%20INR%20478%20crore%20has%20been%20allocated%20under%20MSE-GIFT%20to%20fund%20projects%20related%20to%20renewable%20energy%2C%20clean%20transportation%2C%20energy%20efficiency%20and%20waste%20management%2C%20as%20per%20the%20CII%20Climate%20Action%20Charter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20easing%20financial%20barriers%20that%20prevent%20MSMEs%20from%20adopting%20green%20technologies%2C%20the%20government%20is%20creating%20opportunities%20for%20even%20the%20smallest%20enterprises%20to%20contribute%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20sustainability%20agenda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20Smita%20explains%2C%20aligns%20with%20Rang%20De%E2%80%99s%20overarching%20goal%20of%20supporting%20livelihoods.%20The%20project%20is%20facilitated%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3EPowering%20Livelihoods%20Fund%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20curated%20live%20lending%20platform%20that%20has%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F63836%2Fchetna-gala-sinha-mann-deshi-mahila-bank%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccelerated%20loan%20approvals%20and%20simplified%20financing%20for%20rural%20users%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Frang-de-creating-sustainable-livlihoods-2_11zon-1756211365.jpg%5C%22%20wi