use%20locals%20began%20maintaining%20them.%20%E2%80%9CThat%E2%80%99s%20the%20real%20victory.%20If%20even%20one%20person%20changes%20their%20habits%20after%20watching%20me%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20worth%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20also%20why%20he%20resists%20being%20seen%20as%20the%20hero%20of%20the%20story.%20When%20people%20ask%20to%20join%20him%2C%20he%20gently%20redirects%20them%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20follow%20me.%20Start%20your%20own%20initiative.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGoing%20viral%20and%20staying%20grounded%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20Lazar%20quietly%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F488937%2Fmohammad-aamir-khan-green-wave-waste-to-health-composting-startup-kulgam-kashmir%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epicked%20up%20trash%3C%2Fa%3E%20wherever%20he%20went.%20During%20his%20six%20years%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20he%20organised%20over%2020%20small%20cleanup%20drives.%20Later%2C%20as%20he%20travelled%20across%20South%20India%20and%20to%20Rishikesh%20for%20a%20yoga%20retreat%2C%20he%20carried%20this%20habit%20with%20him%20%E2%80%94%20cleaning%20streets%20with%20the%20help%20of%20a%20few%20locals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Delhi%2C%20he%20joined%20hands%20with%20an%20independent%20civic-tech%20platform%20called%201%20Management%20to%20clean%20the%20elaborate%20stretch%20in%20front%20of%20India%20Gate.%20He%20has%20also%20collaborated%20with%20Instagram%20personalities%2C%20ensuring%20that%20his%20message%20of%20a%20cleaner%20India%20reaches%20a%20wider%20audience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-instagram%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDNUSpaPTEQn%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_emb