EBuilt%20with%20the%20community%2C%20for%20the%20community%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20defining%20feature%20of%20the%20Urban%20Flood%20Management%20System%20is%20the%20citizen-facing%20%E2%80%98Varuna%E2%80%99%20app%2C%20which%20will%20allow%20residents%20to%20receive%20flood%20alerts%20and%20report%20issues%20instantly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20residents%20like%20Ratna%2C%20the%20helpline%20number%20altered%20her%20sense%20of%20helplessness.%20%E2%80%9CNow%2C%20if%20I%20see%20blocked%20drains%20or%20rising%20water%2C%20I%20report%20it%20immediately%2C%20and%20municipal%20teams%20respond%20quickly.%20I%20finally%20feel%20at%20peace.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-12T120614.344_11zon-1754980588.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Canarys%20Automations%20sends%20its%20field%20engineers%20directly%20to%20waterlogged%20areas%20and%20known%20hotspots%20during%20rain%20events%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-12T120614.344_11zon-1754980588.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-12T120614.344_11zon-1754980588-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-12T120614.344_11zon-1754980588-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-12T120614.344_11zon-1754980588-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Busi