-12T121340.915_11zon-1754981038-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-485285%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMunicipal%20teams%20conduct%20pre-rain%20drain%20clean-up%20operations%2C%20schedule%20pump%20maintenance%2C%20and%20pre-position%20mobile%20pumps%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESheshadri%20remarks%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20the%20integration%20of%20real-time%20data%2C%20automated%20pump%20control%2C%20and%20direct%20community%20inputs%20that%20creates%20a%20responsive%20ecosystem.%20This%20coordination%20is%20exactly%20why%20we%20are%20seeing%20quicker%20action%20on%20the%20ground%20and%20reduced%20flood-related%20damage%20across%20the%20city.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20%3Cem%3ESafayi%20%3C%2Fem%3EInspector%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CRather%20than%20chasing%20complaints%20after%20chaos%20begins%2C%20we%20now%20receive%20early%20alerts%20that%20allow%20us%20to%20act%20before%20flooding%20even%20starts.%20Based%20on%20predictions%20from%20the%20system%2C%20we%20reach%20vulnerable%20hotspots%20at%20least%20a%20day%20in%20advance%2C%20mobilising%20sanitation%20workers%20to%20clean%20drains%2C%20clear%20blockages%2C%20and%20ensure%20pumps%20are%20operational.%20If%20required%2C%20we%20also%20deploy%20mobile%20pumps%20to%20reinforce%20these%20efforts.%20This%20proactive%20coordination%20does%20not%20just%20save%20time%2C%20it%20prevents%20water%20from%20entering%20homes%20and%20ultimately%20helps%20protect%20lives.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EStrong%20leadership%20made%20it%20possible%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmbedding%20such%20a%20system%20requires%20committed%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMayor%20Dr.%20Manglesh%20Kumar%20Srivastava%20states%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Urban%20Flood%20Management%20System%20gives%20us%20tools%20to%20anticipate%20floods%20and%20act%20proactively%2C%20not%20only%20protecting%20properties%20but%20restoring%20c