%20were%20rolled%20out%2C%20and%20community%20participation%20increased%20%E2%80%94%20marking%20Gorakhpur%E2%80%99s%20shift%20from%20reactive%20pumping%20to%20intelligent%20flood%20resilience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EResults%20that%20speak%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20has%20been%20visible%20both%20in%20numbers%20and%20lives%20saved%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EResponse%20times%20dropped%20from%2010-12%20hours%20to%20under%201.5-2%20hours.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPump%20downtime%20decreased%20by%20over%2060%25.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPre-monsoon%20drain%20cleaning%20covered%20over%2095%25%20of%20the%20targeted%20areas.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFlood%20forecast%20accuracy%20remained%20above%2080%25%20for%2024-hour%20predictions.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOver%20250%20citizen%20complaints%20were%20recorded%3B%20more%20than%2070%25%20resolved%20within%20hours.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOverall%20system%20efficiency%20improved%20by%2065%25%2C%20boosting%20municipal%20response%20capacity.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERatna%20Devi%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%202022%2C%20whenever%20it%20rained%20heavily%2C%20our%20home%20would%20flood.%20Water%20would%20enter%20the%20kitchen%20and%20the%20living%20room.%20But%20after%20the%20system%20was%20deployed%20in%20our%20area%2C%20everything%20changed.%20We%20got%20timely%20warnings%2C%20the%20pumps%20were%20switched%20on%20even%20before%20the%20rain%20peaked%2C%20and%20even%20if%20some%20water%20did%20enter%20the%20street%2C%20it%20drained%20away%20within%20an%20hour.%20We%20finally%20felt%20like%20the%20city%20was%20prepared%20to%20combat%20prolonged%20rainfall.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20lies%20ahead%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20ahead%2C%20Mayor%20Srivastava%20envisions%20a%20more%20resilient%20Gorakhpur.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20expand%20this%20Urban%20Flood%20Management%20System%2C%20deploy%20more%20sensors